  "title" : "GDG base creation using Java",
  "body" : "<p>From Java z/OS, using zfile I can create a mainframe dataset.  Both flat file and GDG versions.</p>\n<p>If the GDG base does not exist the java code abends. Do we have an option to create the mainframe GDG base dataset from Java?</p>\n"
